== 栽培 ==
[[File:Dicentra.spectabilis.closeup.jpg|thumb]]
[[File:Lamprocapnos_spectabilis_pods.jpg|thumb]]
荷包牡丹生长於温带较凉爽地区，喜阳光散射的半阴环境，较耐寒，怕高温暴晒，因此盛夏休眠期要置於通风良好的荫蔽处。喜湿润，但怕积水，因此要保持土壤半墒，过湿则烂根，过干则叶黄，而盛夏和冬季[[休眠期|休眠期]]要保持土壤微润；喜多[[腐殖质|腐殖质]]的疏松肥沃中性或弱碱性土壤，而沙土和粘土也可生长，不过会生长不良；喜肥，宜施用少量有机肥或三元[[复合肥|复合肥]]，花蕾显色後停肥，休眠期不施肥。<ref name="ShiYang">{{zh}}{{cite journal zh|author=佚名|date=2005|title=《荷包牡丹的莳养》|journal=科学大观园|volume=|issue=7|url=http://www.bast.net.cn/bjkpzc/tszr/zwdg/yhxd/35598.htm|accessdate=2009-02-01|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090109154915/http://www.bast.net.cn/bjkpzc/tszr/zwdg/yhxd/35598.htm|archivedate=2009-01-09}}</ref>可[[播种|播种]]、[[扦插|扦插]]或[[營養繁殖|分株]]繁殖，可在早春或深秋栽培。嫁接荷包牡丹可选用多年生[[芍药|芍药]]作[[砧木|砧木]]。<ref>{{zh}}{{cite web |url=http://www.foodmate.net/topic/324/105074.html |title=根接法救活荷包牡丹 |publisher=食品伙伴网 |date=2008-03-08 |accessdate=2009-02-01 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305152322/http://www.foodmate.net/topic/324/105074.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>虫害有[[蚜虫|蚜虫]]、[[蛞蝓|蛞蝓]]、[[蜗牛|蜗牛]]和[[介壳虫|介壳虫]]，病害有[[叶斑病|叶斑病]]。<ref>{{zh}}{{cite web |date=2006-03-05 |title=荷包牡丹的栽培技术 |publisher=农博花木 |url=http://flower.aweb.com.cn/2006/3/5/1120060305034600.shtml |accessdate=2009-02-02 |archive-date=2016-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160411170412/http://flower.aweb.com.cn/2006/3/5/1120060305034600.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

荷包牡丹有数个栽培种，其中包括白花荷包牡丹以及[[英国|英国]]栽培种“金心”（''{{lang|la|Dicentra spectabilis}}'' {{lang|en|'Goldheart'}}）。“金心”於1997年培育，特点是其嫩黄色的叶子在盛夏时会变为黄绿色。

== 药用 ==
[[File:Lamprocapnos_spectabilis_seeds.jpg|thumb]]
荷包牡丹根可作为解毒活血镇痛的[[中药材|中药材]]使用，在《岭南采药录》中记载荷包牡丹根能散血、消疮毒、除风、和血，药性为辛、苦、温，归肝经，内服可用於治疗[[金疮|金疮]]、[[疮毒|疮毒]]、[[胃痛|胃痛]]，外敷可用於治疗跌打肿痛<ref name="ShiYang"/>，正如汪连仕《采药书》中所载“用其根捣汁，酒冲服之，令人沉醉，金疮之圣药也。”<ref>{{zh}}{{cite web |url=http://www.tcmlib.com/zy/html59/showdetail-353832342ce88db7e58c85e789a1e4b8b9e6a0b92c7a79.html |title=荷包牡丹根的功效 |publisher=意古中医 |accessdate=2009-02-01 }}{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>

不过，荷包牡丹全草有潜在毒性<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.pfaf.org/database/plants.php?Dicentra+spectabilis |title=''Dicentra spectabilis'' |publisher=Plants For A Future |accessdate=2009-02-01 |archive-date=2009-01-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090117145758/http://www.pfaf.org/database/plants.php?Dicentra+spectabilis |dead-url=no }}</ref>，部分人接触此植物会有皮肤刺痛感，源自{{link-en|荷包牡丹碱|Bicuculline}}和{{link-en|原阿片碱|Protopine}}等[[异喹啉|异喹啉]]类生物碱的作用<ref>{{en}}{{cite web |url=http://www.uvm.edu/~pass/perry/oh63harm.html |title=Potentially Harmful Perennials OH 63 |accessdate=2009-02-01 |author=Leonard P. Perry |date=1997-02-28 |publisher=Perry's Perennial Pages |archive-date=2009-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090305231620/http://www.uvm.edu/~pass/perry/oh63harm.html |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name=Leikin2007>{{en}}{{Cite book en | editor =Jerrold B. Leikin; Frank P. Paloucek | date = 2007 | title = Poisoning and toxicology handbook | pages = 886 | isbn = 1420044796 | publisher = CRC | location = Boca Raton, Fla }}</ref>，因此要注意用量，否则可能出现[[呕吐|呕吐]]、[[腹泻|腹泻]]、[[呼吸衰竭|呼吸衰竭]]、[[心脏麻痹|心脏麻痹]]等症状。

